regular vs Purecomponent

regular: a regular component doest not implement the shouldComponentUpdate() method. it alwasys returnaa true by default.

pure: a pure component on the other hand implements shouldComponentUpdate() method with shallow props and state comparison.

shallow comparison

primitive type: a (sc) b return true if a and b have the same value and are of the same type.

complex type: a (sc) b return true if a and b refdrence the exact same object.

